     Sequence DFill02B
     Volume m
     Tone HighTom1
     Rtime 2
     RVolume 10
End

Begin Drum-MediumTom
     Sequence DFill02C
     Volume m
     Tone MidTom1
     Rtime 2
     RVolume 10
End

Begin Drum-FloorTom
     Sequence DFill02D
     Volume m
     Tone LowTom1
     Rtime 2
     RVolume 10
End

Begin Scale-Bass
     Sequence Scale4
     Voice FingeredBass
     Octave 3
     Volume mf
     Rtime 2
     RVolume 5
