Drum-Cymbal Sequence -
Drum-Snare Sequence D1234-2 z
Drum-Kick Sequence D1234 D1
Drum-HH Sequence -
Bass Sequence -
Chord-Piano Sequence C1234 C1
Plectrum-Guitar Sequence PD24 PD1

Begin Drum-FloorTom
     Sequence D1234-2 z 
     Volume m
     Tone LowTom1
     Rtime 2
     RVolume 10
End

Begin Drum-Crash
     Sequence z D1
     Volume m
     Tone CrashCymbal1
     Rtime 2
     RVolume 10
